FBIS3-33385 "drlat036_m_94017" FBIS-LAT-94-036 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Feb 1994 Brazil Russians Visit To Learn About Hyperinflation PY2202153194 Sao Paulo O ESTADO DE SAO PAULO in Portuguese 20 Feb 94 p B6 PY2202153194 Sao Paulo O ESTADO DE SAO PAULO Language: Portuguese Article Type:BFN [Article by Isabel Dias de Aguiar] [Excerpt] Brazilians' ability to live with a high inflation rate has caught the attention of people outside our borders. A Russian banking delegation, representing 10 financial institutions, arrived in Sao Paulo in early February with the objective of learning a little bit of the know-how [previous word in English] Brazilians have developed in this regard. The delegation's objective is to learn how to operate a financial system with hyperinflation. [passage omitted]
